ji\" /><br />\n好矛盾"},{"pid":"adeec356ec1005fa124c1cab8447f473e88fe9c5","tid":228280,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去馬啦，唔溝會令自己後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我唔想去完馬之後後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好矛盾</blockquote><br />\n屌 講起就燥<br />\n最鳩憎呢挺男人<br />\n話唔撚上心<br />\n但又唔比我講鳩佢壞話<br />\n明明條臭閪搞小動作比我睇<br />\n仲鬧返我轉頭覺得我有心病<br />\n咁咪下世投胎做返佢隻狗囉屌"},{"pid":"01f32a01c1443feb67f20a0c8814ba8be15997c8","tid":228280,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去馬啦，唔溝會令自己後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我唔想去完馬之後後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好矛盾</blockquote><br />\n屌 講起就燥<br />\n最鳩憎呢挺男人<br />\n話唔撚上心<br />\n但又唔比我講鳩佢壞話<br />\n明明條臭閪搞小動作比我睇<br />\n仲鬧返我轉頭覺得我有心病<br />\n咁咪下世投胎做返佢隻狗囉屌</blockquote><br />\n佢地5年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚把閉咩<br />\n我唔係大撚曬就咪撚嘥我時間"},{"pid":"5d8d0a4265270563888f8d956d13f626b73d136a","tid":228280,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去馬啦，唔溝會令自己後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我唔想去完馬之後後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好矛盾</blockquote><br />\n屌 講起就燥<br />\n最鳩憎呢挺男人<br />\n話唔撚上心<br />\n但又唔比我講鳩佢壞話<br />\n明明條臭閪搞小動作比我睇<br />\n仲鬧返我轉頭覺得我有心病<br />\n咁咪下世投胎做返佢隻狗囉屌</blockquote><br />\n佢地5年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚把閉咩<br />\n我唔係大撚曬就咪撚嘥我時間</blockquote><br />\n如果我啲